{
  "texts": [
    "Training BLOOM, a model slightly larger and substantially more energy-efficient than GPT-3, produces 50.5 metric tons of CO2e 12.",
    "Apart from the amortized emissions associated with training, each AI system query also contributes to the overall emission footprint.",
    "An informal online estimate for ChatGPT indicates that it produces 0.382 g CO2e per query 18, based on 3.82 metric tons CO2e per day divided by 10,000,000 queries per day.",
    "In comparison, a deployment of BLOOM generated 1.5 g per query (340 kg CO2e divided by 230,768 queries) 12.",
    "Assuming that ChatGPT undergoes a full re-training of the model once per month and continues with an estimated 10,000,000 queries per day, the 552 metric tons divided by 300,000,000 queries equates to 1.84 g CO2e per query for the amortized training cost."
  ]
}